         MACRO                                                                  
&L       SEGB  &LOC,&LEN,&SEGCB                                                 
         AIF   ('&LOC&LEN' NE '').SEG                                           
&L       SEG   (R1),0,&SEGCB,B                                                  
         MEXIT                                                                  
.SEG     ANOP                                                                   
&L       SEG   &LOC,&LEN,&SEGCB,B                                               
         MEND                                                                   
